title: Raisinghani vs Raisinghani
overview: Raisinghani vs Raisinghani focuses on a sharp-witted young lawyer making her mark in her father's law firm, a suave and driven contender and a young intern harbouring a dark secret as their lives intricately weave together at a law firm in a legal tale of ambition and intrigue. The riveting courtroom drama explores moral dilemmas and the choice of the right over easy.
